天奴加盟既？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n純粹唔啱位<br />\n最好人選就係大佬同華拉提，不過黎到機會同你係絲打一樣都係0<br />\n<br />\n呢兩個人可以做番調控球隊角色，而古天奴個位美斯已經做緊，係巴西隊唔見得古同尼合作得好好"},{"pid":"c56dc9df0b610fd67f82712b22a08866458b1d47","tid":244183,"uid":82786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T10:55:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>認真想問下巴迷<br />\n點解好似咁唔想古天奴加盟既？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實前面有msn已經好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔使再要多個攻擊球員<br />\n反而要個控制到中場節奏嘅球員重要好多<br />\n本身ff過普巴會過黎 因為佢腳法 身體有曬 好適合巴塞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08a65774cabc3e46bf01ae83a4a6544d015f12e8","tid":244183,"uid":993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T10:57:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>認真想問下巴迷<br />\n點解好似咁唔想古天奴加盟既？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實前面有msn已經好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔使再要多個攻擊球員<br />\n反而要個控制到中場節奏嘅球員重要好多<br />\n本身ff過普巴會過黎 因為佢腳法 身體有曬 好適合巴塞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n當初係高登得我同鳩白支持買普巴，結果比人圍插<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n宜家真係抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3abc898589d7f97522a2631eba2b8b75ca0d3c00","tid":244183,"uid":311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T10:58:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>認真想問下巴迷<br />\n點解好似咁唔想古天奴加盟既？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n純粹唔啱位<br />\n最好人選就係大佬同華拉提，不過黎到機會同你係絲打一樣都係0<br />\n<br />\n呢兩個人可以做番調控球隊角色，而古天奴個位美斯已經做緊，係巴西隊唔見得古同尼合作得好好</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw 我100%真絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a00c14a4ec091da02e1451e5109d5a8924f81ca","tid":244183,"uid":82786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T11:15:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>認真想問下巴迷<br />\n點解好似咁唔想古天奴加盟既？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實前面有msn已經好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔使再要多個攻擊球員<br />\n反而要個控制到中場節奏嘅球員重要好多<br />\n本身ff過普巴會過黎 因為佢腳法 身體有曬 好適合巴塞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n當初係高登得我同鳩白支持買普巴，結果比人圍插<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n宜家真係抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唉 點知普巴居然愛回家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢如果有得過黎巴塞 一定唔會踢到好似係曼聯咁柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係摩連奴手下浪費曬佢進攻天份 下下打到就住就住  曼聯又冇人壓得住佢 得伊巴一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去到巴塞成件事真係會唔同曬<br />\n中前場全部世界級球星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8123ba38a7f20ad61189cd391f1e72a8219c9ba","tid":244183,"uid":38144,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T11:24:14.000Z","msg":"普巴有話想去巴？<br />\n講到想買就有咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1923665dc5057f3d46943367b904d924e97d6426","tid":244183,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T11:28:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>普巴有話想去巴？<br />\n講到想買就有咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n恰慣d 西甲隊以為我曼好蝦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b210ad3d9c05b12d0bf2c433249f43d1ccc078b4","tid":244183,"uid":82786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-0